    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示主分支和两个特性分支的合并场景。主分支要有初始提交a，然后从主分支分出feature-1和feature-2这两个分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit a",
        "branch feature-1",
        "branch feature-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。关于分支的显示顺序，您希望feature-1和feature-2怎么排列？还有，需要显示提交标签吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "mainBranchOrder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "feature-1放在最左边，feature-2在中间，main在最右边。需要显示提交标签，这样方便看commit id。另外把日志级别设成debug，方便我们检查配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature-1 order: 0",
        "feature-2 order: 1",
        "main order: 2",
        "logLevel: debug",
        "showCommitLabel: true"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已配置好初始化参数，分支顺序和标签显示都设置好了。现在开始画：主分支先有提交a，然后分出feature-1和feature-2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init",
        "commit id:\"a\"",
        "branch feature-1",
        "branch feature-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "feature-2上做两次提交，id分别是f和g。然后切换到feature-1做一次提交x。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id:\"f\"",
        "commit id:\"g\"",
        "checkout feature-1",
        "commit id:\"x\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：feature-2有f和g两个提交，然后切到feature-1做提交x。之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature-2 commits",
        "feature-1 commit x"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后切回main做提交b，最后把feature-2合并到main。这样整个流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit id:\"b\"",
        "merge feature-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。main分支现在有提交a、b，以及从feature-2合并进来的f、g。feature-1独立在左边有提交x，没有参与合并。您看这样对吗？",
